      "date": "2021-12-01 03:35:15.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nkernel config files generate method:\n===================================\nrpm -iv https://vault.centos.org/8.5.2111/BaseOS/Source/SPackages/kernel-4.18.0-348.2.1.el8_5.src.rpm\nrpmbuild -bp --nodeps  --target=`uname -m` ./SPECS/kernel.spec\ncp ~/rpmbuild/BUILD/kernel-4.18.0-348.2.1.el8_5/linux-4.18.0-348.2.1.el8.aarch64/configs/kernel-4.18.0-aarch64.config kernel-4.18.0-4.18-rhel8.5-aarch64.config\ncp ~/rpmbuild/BUILD/kernel-4.18.0-305.19.1.el8_4/linux-4.18.0-305.19.1.el8.aarch64/configs/kernel-4.18.0-aarch64.config kernel-4.18.0-4.18-rhel8.4-aarch64.config\nremove first line \"# arm64\"\n\n\n sh autogen.sh && ./configure -C --enable-dist && make dist\n ../lustre-release/contrib/lbuild/lbuild --ccache --kerneldir=/home/centos/kernel  --lustre=/home/centos/work/lustre-release/lustre-2.14.55_169_g0f9e2dd.tar.gz  --target=4.18-rhel8.4 --distro=rhel8.4\n ../lustre-release/contrib/lbuild/lbuild --ccache --kerneldir=/home/centos/kernel  --lustre=/home/centos/work/lustre-release/lustre-2.14.55_169_g0f9e2dd.tar.gz  --target=4.18-rhel8.5 --distro=rhel8.5",
